EASTERN CARIBBEAN SEA.
TEN METER LONG F/V GWADA FISH, BLUE HULL WITH WHITE STRIPE,
THREE PERSONS ON BOARD, OVERDUE POINTE A PITRE (16-14N 061-31W)
AND RETURN. VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP
LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO MRCC FORT DE FRANCE,
